profile:
Iron Art by Robert Aucoin 
Custom metal furniture, custom railings, custom iron gates, custom lighting, custom accessories and more. 
Working closely with designers, architects, artisans and home owners to create one of a kind designs in a variety of metals.  
Stainless steel, mild steel, aluminum, copper, bronze and brass are all used.
From concept to completion, Robert will design, sketch, prototype and create a signed finished product.  
If you have your own design, Robert will work with you to create your the idea to life.

For an onsite quote or to make an appointment, please call 613 376 6359
